text: Gennes-Longuefuye is a commune in the Mayenne department in north-western France. It was established on 1 January 2019 by merger of the former communes of Gennes-sur-Glaize (the seat) and Longuefuye.Arrêté préfectoral 14 November 2018 ==See also== *Communes of the Mayenne department ==References== Genneslonguefuye Category:Populated places established in 2019
title: Gennes-Longuefuye
